<h4>Page Rules</h4>
<p>Page Rules provide you with fine-grained control of Wave Telecom on each page of your site. You can enable full HTML caching, individually customize Wave Telecom’s features on a page by page basis or enable edge network forwarding to improve page delivery even further.</p>
