<p>If you get a surge in traffic, Wave Telecom’s CDN will absorb the effect so your server stays online. On average, you\'ll see 65% fewer requests to your servers and save 60% of your bandwidth, even with Wave Telecom\'s free plan.</p>
</div>
<div class="hrSolid"></div>
<div class="large-icon-magic-wand article-icons-img"></div>
<div class="article-icons">
<h4>Automatic IPv6</h4>
<p>Make your site available to visitors on IPv6 networks with the click of a button. No need to rush to upgrade your infrastructure. Keep your IPv4 infrastructure until you\'re ready, we\'ll make it seem to the world you\'re running a modern dual-stack.</p>
