<div class="hrSolid"></div>
<div class="large-icon-handshake article-icons-img"></div>
<div class="article-icons-last">
<h4>Works with other CDNs</h4>
<p>If you’re already using a CDN, Wave Telecom works as a complement. You have the choice of routing CDN traffic through Wave Telecom first (saving you bandwidth &amp; money) or bypassing Wave Telecom altogether for your CDN traffic.</p>
